"無國界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"},{"pid":"f08403b300e9b6a32f52e92ed7920856eb2fab3a","tid":1740572,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c861ff9224a4985a379b289c9ae13349f068be4b","tid":1740572,"uid":23385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4f84e9d8c107c70776aaaad2a8ca5ae2be0e2142","tid":1740572,"uid":50744,"like":263,"dislike":0,"score":263,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"會飛去搞非洲小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"非洲幻幻要用身體換食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"性交轉運d fd黎"},{"pid":"781d9f5cf8251139f648fa7924045b978eb9e859","tid":1740572,"uid":237562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4f84e9d8c107c70776aaaad2a8ca5ae2be0e2142","tid":1740572,"uid":50744,"like":263,"dislike":0,"score":263,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:39:33.000Z","msg":"會飛去搞非洲小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:55:08.000Z","msg":"捐錢比佢玩童妓"},{"pid":"b0505be624869d7e0d957350f404bc38fac040cf","tid":1740572,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781d9f5cf8251139f648fa7924045b978eb9e859","tid":1740572,"uid":237562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4f84e9d8c107c70776aaaad2a8ca5ae2be0e2142","tid":1740572,"uid":50744,"like":263,"dislike":0,"score":263,"cite